---
import Layout from "#/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" class="p-4 sm:p-8">
  <article class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <p class="lead">
      Chat with Dice is a lightweight online space for people playing low-prep
      and no-prep tabletop role-playing games.
    </p>

    <p>
      It combines group chat with straightforward dice rolling and small,
      system-specific tools for tracking the things that matter during play. The
      aim is to make joining and running a game fast and obvious on phones,
      tablets, and desktop computers, without expecting elaborate maps or
      prepared art assets.
    </p>

    <h2>Open source</h2>
    <p>
      Chat with Dice is open-source software. You can inspect the code, report
      problems, and follow development in the
      <a href="https://github.com/lumphammer/chat-with-dice">
        lumphammer/chat-with-dice GitHub repository
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2>More information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/terms">Read the terms of service</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact us or send feedback</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>
